{"tid":1490954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求，缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:05:15.000Z","uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb23bb296cea831b79c21910e0c74b856de33e9c","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一，防止赤化，香港自治<br />\n撤回惡法一，都會有惡法二，自治係唯一根治方法<br />\n<br />\n二，撤銷政治檢控<br />\n司法機構不應成為維穩工具<br />\n<br />\n三，撤回暴動定性<br />\n沒有暴徒只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n四，重設監警制度<br />\n失效既執法機構監管制度引致警權過大，甚至失去控制，必須徹底清除腐肉，重組警隊<br />\n<br />\n五，落實雙普選<br />\n不接受任何框架任何限期，即時執行雙普選"},{"pid":"0d2de05751c6f4e3130b3e18d7367f604bf65024","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"酷刑個度我都好撚燥，但唔好全部focus都擺落黑警度，記住我地既五大訴求"},{"pid":"81c24bd23a2197c9b2ca22347b40f6f9ffea08da","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"536bf28976861b78799850d559b35db9623a75a1","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"e0f98f057a4bbdddc5d5590b3f4760582fd8ae57","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"8946e98bf47d164699e0ffed87318dac6bacfc2b","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"63df06e5bbfb6fc6e2f77cd9a9136c83279e76ee","tid":1490954,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"f374f3552e643855c299b55a0f74a73cdf108b80","tid":1490954,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1490061/page/1\" data-auto-